---
title: Irish Sirloin Steak in Truffle Mushroom Sauce with creamy mash and pan-fried veg
description: The mash that accompanies the juicy sirloin and garlicky veg in this dish is rich and perfectly creamy. Truffle oil imbues the dish with plenty of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R13_W32_IE_IESB16809-3_MAIN_high-295f374b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/664f2d238606e082f188773a-en-IE.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 595 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 9.5 g
